Hi Neodoc !

Here is the link to the most complete Shaman Epic Walkthrough. Hoping this will help you. 

-> <A HREF="http://www.eqshaman.com/epic/" TARGET="_BLANK">http://www.eqshaman.com/epic/</A>

My advice is :

1) 3 full groups 50+ OR
2) 2 full groups 55+ OR EVEN
3) 1 full group 60+ 

IMPORTANT : One rogue with 200 or above in lockpicking is ABSOLUTLY necessary to enter the building.

If you got uber friends used to play with each other, then the second and third solutions are do-able (especialy if you got a 60+ wizard to nuke and a 60+ cleric to group heal). 

Lord Ghiosk hit fast and hard and got quite a lot of HP. The other prob why you will need so many people is that you will have to enter the building (rogue with 200 in lockpicking required) and clear the path. Lord Ghiosk spawn from a dead reaver so you will have to fight them in hope to make him spawn (see my other post about blackreavers because they can manage you some really bad surprises).

